  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main purpose of this study is to assess the effect of a cognitive group intervention on
      prevention of major depression in 14-15-year-old adolescents. Moreover, the effect on other
      selected mental health parameters are investigated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
